# =============================================================================
# BULLETPROOF .GITIGNORE - PERIOD TRACKER PROJECT
# Tech Stack: FastAPI (Python) + Next.js (Node.js) + Docker + PostgreSQL + ML
# Purpose: Prevent secret leaks and exclude build artifacts
# =============================================================================

# =============================================================================
# SECTION 1: SECRETS & ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES (CRITICAL - NEVER COMMIT THESE)
# =============================================================================

